cppproject: A python script to create a single cross-platform C++
project from platform specific projects

Invoke cppproject as follows:

cppproject --visualstudio=<visualstudio_project_directory> --xcode=<code_project_directory> --makefile=<location_of_makefile> --project-root=<location of the project root director> project_name

For example if you want to create a project called hello with 3
platform specific projects hello_vs hello_xcode hello_makefile 
